去從未主動採取行動，亦未曾在電郵中提及要確保「一中」原則。而「台灣旗」就是指「青天白日滿地紅」中華民國國旗。<br />\n<br />\n房署發言人傍晚回覆《立場新聞》查詢，指一般不評論內部的電郵通訊，並指不時向前線人員發出電郵提示其執行職務，會按既定指引跟進和移除未經批准的展示品 ."},{"pid":"903b6a2b78a1783f00500ba75132dff6efb50144","tid":2234454,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T15:46:28.000Z","msg":"聽日有咩活動?"},{"pid":"b7a6ea94881706421e681351e098fb5d8bb2f183","tid":2234454,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"903b6a2b78a1783f00500ba75132dff6efb50144","tid":2234454,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T15:46:28.000Z","msg":"聽日有咩活動?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T17:29:56.000Z","msg":"我都想知"},{"pid":"2ef550410543b9c9b76f7026c4226ff9b85d7433","tid":2234454,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:04:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-tw/news/world/%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E8%A7%B8%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9F-%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E6%9B%9D%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E8%A9%95%E6%96%B7%E6%A8%99%E6%BA%96/ar-BB16gfKC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2597%2597%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25A7%25B8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25EF%25BC%259F-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259B%259D%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%2597%259C%25E8%25A9%2595%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%25A8%2599%25E6%25BA%2596%2Far-BB16gfKC&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5AzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=233fcd71\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/zh-tw/news/world/%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E8%A7%B8%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9F-%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E6%9B%9D%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E8%A9%95%E6%96%B7%E6%A8%99%E6%BA%96/ar-BB16gfKC</a><br />\n<br />\n而法新社記者泰勒（Jerome Taylor）在推特（Twitter）上發文，引述港警說法表示，僅展示或擁有中華民國國旗，並不觸犯《香港國安法》；但若是